sted by rotational shearing, removes the field component\ntransverse to the PIL and causes the fibrils to coalesce into long PIL-aligned\nfilaments.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 22 Mar 2011 20:35:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-27"}
