gorithm for our robust lattice alignment method by using the\nexisting iterative IA algorithm that was designed for the conventional IA\nmethod. Numerical results verify the advantages of the proposed robust lattice\nalignment method.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 23 Mar 2011 14:18:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-27"}
