theory, despite the corresponding gauge boson\nhaving a mass. Our results reduce to those of other authors in the special\ncases where there is no kinetic mixing or there is no direct coupling to\nordinary fermions, such as for recently proposed dark-matter scenarios.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 23 Mar 2011 15:43:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 26 May 2011 17:41:22 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 28 Jan 2013 17:17:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-27"}
